snippet.textDisplay: Nice "Making of", but a bit late: Is this delayed production and release a hint that Coke Studio India and/or Armaan Malik are  planing a continuation of this hit with a new K-pop/I-Pop coop?There is even  a video "Behind the scenes" released close to the publication of the original song, so there is no reason to drop another one without purpose. But may be it's only a christmas gift.   By the way: the editor of this video falsely claimed in a subtitle that Armann Malik is not only the main vocalist of this song, but also the composer: that's no true, following the credits of the original song. There we read that the song is composed by the DJ Duo Lost Stories (Hindi and Telugu part) & ELLY (korean and english part); the lyrics are written by Kunaal Vermaa, Elly & ShinsadongTiger. The music was produced by Lost Stories & S.Tiger.
